"title": "8452: neighbours, duty to",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8452: neighbours, duty to",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture defines the identity of neighbours in various ways, and indicates the nature and extent of believers' obligations to them.</p>\n<h2>Neighbours defined</h2>\n<h3>Those who live nearby</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:29\">PRO 3:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:22\">EXO 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod12:4\">EXO 12:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut19:14\">DEU 19:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:3\">2KI 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov27:10\">PRO 27:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke15:4-Luke15:6\">LUK 15:4–15:6</a></p>\n<h3>Those of the same race</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:18\">LEV 19:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam15:27-1Sam15:28\">1SA 15:27–15:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam28:17\">1SA 28:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr12:38-1Chr12:40\">1CH 12:38–12:40</a></p>\n<h3>Peoples of surrounding nations</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:7\">DEU 1:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh9:16\">JOS 9:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:14\">1SA 7:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra9:1\">EZR 9:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:30\">NEH 9:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:28\">NEH 10:28</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:31\">NEH 10:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps76:11\">PSA 76:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:26\">EZK 16:26</a></p>\n<h3>Those who show mercy to people in need</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:29-Luke10:37\">LUK 10:29–10:37</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Fellow Christians</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:25\">EPH 4:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:1-Rom15:2\">ROM 15:1–15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:13-Gal5:16\">GAL 5:13–5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:11-Jas4:12\">JAS 4:11–4:12</a></p>\n<h2>Duties to neighbours</h2>\n<h3>Love</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:34-Matt22:39\">MAT 22:34–22:39</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:28-Mark12:34\">MRK 12:28–12:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:25-Luke10:28\">LUK 10:25–10:28</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:18\">LEV 19:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">DEU 6:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:19\">MAT 19:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:8-Rom13:10\">ROM 13:8–13:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:14\">GAL 5:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas2:8-Jas2:9\">JAS 2:8–2:9</a></p>\n<h3>Assistance</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod23:4-Exod23:5\">EXO 23:4–23:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:1-Deut22:4\">DEU 22:1–22:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:21\">PRO 14:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt25:34-Matt25:40\">MAT 25:34–25:40</a></p>\n<h3>Fair treatment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod22:14\">EXO 22:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:17\">EXO 20:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev6:2-Lev6:5\">LEV 6:2–6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:15\">LEV 19:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:21\">DEU 5:21</a></p>\n<h3>Honest dealings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:13\">LEV 19:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech8:16-Zech8:17\">ZEC 8:16–8:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:25\">EPH 4:25</a></p>\n<h3>Forgiveness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:32\">EPH 4:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt18:21-Matt18:35\">MAT 18:21–18:35</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:3-Luke17:4\">LUK 17:3–17:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:1-Rom15:2\">ROM 15:1–15:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:13\">COL 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>Reproof</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:17\">LEV 19:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke17:3\">LUK 17:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal6:1-Gal6:2\">GAL 6:1–6:2</a></p>\n<h2>Prohibition of negative actions towards neighbours</h2>\n<h3>False witness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:16\">EXO 20:16</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:20\">DEU 5:20</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev19:16\">LEV 19:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:28\">PRO 24:28</a></p>\n<h3>Oppression</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:13\">JER 22:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:28\">PRO 3:28</a></p>\n<h3>Judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:12\">JAS 4:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:1-Matt7:2\">MAT 7:1–7:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke6:41-Luke6:42\">LUK 6:41–6:42</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom14:13\">ROM 14:13</a></p>",
